Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:23.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}真実は何処へ　探して
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:25.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Where's my soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}It's like a fear　悪い夢の様で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:39.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}目覚めても　All I've got is bones
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}I'm in a panic? Get out, hurry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:44.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Oh, there're mysteries and miseries
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:47.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Dead or alive　狭間に揺られて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:49.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}彷徨えば　Right to left to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}孤独の招待　感情の消退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:54.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}踊る1 2 3 steps on this dark stage
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Raise your flag, march on, fight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:19:00.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}仮面の淵へ　手を掛けどただ骨が鳴るのみ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Wars and swords, tears and blood
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:07.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}溢る力が　不意に嗤い出した
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:13.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}真実は何処へ　探して
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:15.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Where's my soul? Where's my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:18.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}現実に呑まれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:23.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Don't hesitate, go this way
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:25.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}理解らない　構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:28.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}紛い力振るっても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:33.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}ただこの世界を生き抜けよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:38.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}嗚呼　失くした哀しみがまた疼いてく…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:41.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Misery-World
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:51.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}漆黒の空　冷たく　Midnight
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}夜(よ)の闇は　Always drives me mad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:56.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Where is that star now? I found the star now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:59.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}But it's so beautiful, I'm so doubtful
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:01.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}戸惑いの中宿る　Desire
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:04.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}見渡せば　Sky and land and sea
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}高み(ハイ)への誘(いざな)い　絶対の支配
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:09.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}昇れ　1.2.3 steps to the royal throne
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Cast a spell, call them up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:14.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}絶望を呼べ　虚しさに酔い兵達が舞う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Shouts and barks, grief and death
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:21.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}慄く者に　無慈悲を振り降ろせ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:27.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}無情を行け　暴いて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:29.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Break it all, take it all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:32.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}手に入れろ全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:37.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}I just pray, or just play?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}そうじゃない　止まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:42.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}消えない疑念抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:47.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}失くした物を取り戻せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:52.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}嗚呼　それさえ覆う狂気に塗(まみ)れても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:54.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Crazy world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:13.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}見えない心と確かに在る体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:23.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}信じたいものを　己に誓え
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:30.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}真実(こたえ)を捨てて　走れ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:32.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Where's my soul? Where's my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}その意志を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:40.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Don't hesitate, go this way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:43.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}理解(わか)らない　構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:45.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}夢でも現実でも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:50.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}ただこの世界を生き抜こう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:55.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}さあ　何処まででもこの足が行く限り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:58.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}Misery-World
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:23.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}真實在何處  我四處探尋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:25.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}我魂在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}一切猶如一場恐懼噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:39.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}醒來依舊  身剩白骨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}我驚慌失措?  快點消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:44.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}哦  這中充滿謎與不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:47.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}亦死亦生  搖曳於生死邊界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:49.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,160)\blur3}瞬息猶豫  即跌入無底地獄
